{"tid":1639730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不斷指責前線係鬼 再搵狗做鬼 就係想全部人同前線割蓆","createTime":"2019-10-08T16:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:41:41.000Z","uid":112355,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fa00aca0c344469ceafe10078ae2ff0b8002c591","tid":1639730,"uid":112355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:54:22.000Z","msg":"由71爆玻璃 第一次出火魔法<br />\n甚至去到而家裝修港鐵 黑鋪<br />\n都有一大班人話前線勇武手足係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇錯 當中真係有少量係真鬼<br />\n但係佢哋混入示威者當中<br />\n好多時都係為咗去捉前線 而唔係單純帶風向去搞破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係今日呢一隻智障狗 扮手足扮到攞埋黑警專用嘅胡椒噴霧出嚟 點解呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有狗扮市民入已關MTR 破壞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639534</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的就係為咗令到大家真正咁相信 前線勇武就係由黑警打扮</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有喺前線嘅都係黑警 所有升級咗嘅行動都係由黑警煽動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣大家就唔會去支持行動升級 因為真正嘅手足係唔會咁癲乜乜乜...<br />\n慢慢大家就唔會再相信前線 甚至阻止前線做嘢 篤灰等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後運動會因為咁樣而慢慢潰散<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋就係咁樣衰咗喺自己手上</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應對嘅方法好簡單 由六月講到而家<br />\n不篤灰 不割蓆 不分化<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係又有幾多人真係做得到?</span></span><br />\n唔滿意手足爆太多鋪 得 慢慢同佢哋溝通<br />\n叫佢哋爆少啲 又或者淨係爆黨鐵 其他裝飾算<br />\n而唔係一句撻埋去就話佢係鬼<br />\n希望大家唔好當啲口號嗌完就算<br />\n真係不篤灰 不割蓆 不分化好冇?"},{"pid":"cd0dad5197dcd913a8df55dedd24ff3e47851f76","tid":1639730,"uid":311198,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:55:28.000Z","msg":"係 呢幾日不停見到捉鬼post 非常擔心"},{"pid":"0db18426354e252ce40c6a0235a656e83fe2deaa","tid":1639730,"uid":228688,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:56:59.000Z","msg":"冇證據就核彈都唔割，但有曬片影到嘅一定點都唔會幫班狗認左係我地做"},{"pid":"6ff33e6187741d175bba8593d766380f6e81f87e","tid":1639730,"uid":262899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:58:08.000Z","msg":"幫你推～<br />\n<br />\n幫手推一推～ 感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被捕求助（對唔住手足）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633560</a>"},{"pid":"98007178310a05c1fc7b5c9dd9b136c9084d4553","tid":1639730,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7705d9febe391c9e7226378766598354f2ed18bd","tid":1639730,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:01:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"47b5cd8e780d2f2ea90cd8aa20d8393b90748ff1","tid":1639730,"uid":112355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0db18426354e252ce40c6a0235a656e83fe2deaa","tid":1639730,"uid":228688,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:56:59.000Z","msg":"冇證據就核彈都唔割，但有曬片影到嘅一定點都唔會幫班狗認左係我地做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"冇錯 所以今日捉到呢一個 同埋以後斷正係臥底嘅黑警絕對唔應該因為「不捉鬼」而放生<br />\n但係就算前線最後做出嚟嘅效果唔好睇 只要佢真係手足嘅話 咁就唔應該話佢係鬼<br />\n最多事後再檢討"},{"pid":"3830da0ed1694c321b9b3121150986226f8889cd","tid":1639730,"uid":34714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"唔割 但事後賴晒係鬼做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55862886e6d6489bcad9d5f3a7170e8f21e3c6cd","tid":1639730,"uid":288662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3830da0ed1694c321b9b3121150986226f8889cd","tid":1639730,"uid":34714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"唔割 但事後賴晒係鬼做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b7d107bd862a1fe41b7ecbf199108a44e0917f","tid":1639730,"uid":199834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"岩開始已經搵狗做鬼，想我地割，點知我地死都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭講出口，就知佢又想繼續咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db1c312b414f8a3a6428c9c4924e4d129704db0","tid":1639730,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:09:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77a72f76e3e30bd64fc38bdd4b8248ac15b14431","tid":1639730,"uid":112355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3830da0ed1694c321b9b3121150986226f8889cd","tid":1639730,"uid":34714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"唔割 但事後賴晒係鬼做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"咁樣只會令到大家唔願接受前線所做嘅嘢<br />\n試諗下全世界都話掟汽油彈係鬼 你估下仲有冇人敢掟?"},{"pid":"1ff11d032b996ffb89554709fe3a8aa489fe57af","tid":1639730,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77a72f76e3e30bd64fc38bdd4b8248ac15b14431","tid":1639730,"uid":112355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3830da0ed1694c321b9b3121150986226f8889cd","tid":1639730,"uid":34714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"唔割 但事後賴晒係鬼做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"咁樣只會令到大家唔願接受前線所做嘅嘢<br />\n試諗下全世界都話掟汽油彈係鬼 你估下仲有冇人敢掟?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:09:55.000Z","msg":"唔覺"},{"pid":"c7458c00704c21a1b1fe84c7138139d0296df707","tid":1639730,"uid":11448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1ff11d032b996ffb89554709fe3a8aa489fe57af","tid":1639730,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77a72f76e3e30bd64fc38bdd4b8248ac15b14431","tid":1639730,"uid":112355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3830da0ed1694c321b9b3121150986226f8889cd","tid":1639730,"uid":34714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"唔割 但事後賴晒係鬼做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"咁樣只會令到大家唔願接受前線所做嘅嘢<br />\n試諗下全世界都話掟汽油彈係鬼 你估下仲有冇人敢掟?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:09:55.000Z","msg":"唔覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:11:52.000Z","msg":"有啲嘢心照不喧"},{"pid":"4cb518f839ce4fb1ec1ebdf0e6717c7e6fef4545","tid":1639730,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:12:20.000Z","msg":"[member]但我真係見到有手足有光環? 有臂有環<br />\n背囊都有個顏色環<br />\n真係要避免/member]"},{"pid":"fc83a8bf94e62989fa8a5cd44f9a527b4cfcd7f5","tid":1639730,"uid":163485,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:20:21.000Z","msg":"咁有D真係證據十足係狗做鬼<br />\n可能係佢地以揾狗做鬼D人會割<br />\n但事實係唔會,因為前線做野係有原因,有目的性向政權丶黑社會施壓,<br />\n但班狗就唔知做乜,9破壞,仲要好多次俾人影到出入狗局,狗車,同狗講係自己人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">狗就係狗,係扮唔到人</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d1d5538665b3439d69454d1594f32a2ca19252dc","tid":1639730,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:28:39.000Z","msg":"放心喎，民意早已歸邊，呢個地步好難割架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而係我哋要堅持繼續推片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續帶風向就真！<br />\n<br />\n警察扮示威者片唔少，但要時間慢慢刻落市民個腦度，特別係冇立場、淺黃嗰浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲係要耐啲時間先睇到成效嘅，繼續share出去就冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b206b98ab6a956897b018